  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Treatment of chronic medium-severe periodontitis with mesenchymal stem cells and mesenchymal
      stem cells predifferentiated in osteogenic direction
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The bone defect will be filled with a porous membrane based on bone collagen measuring 5x5 mm
      or more with mesenchymal stem cells and mesenchymal stem cells predifferentiated in
      osteogenic direction
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
